Jumping Shell is an exhilarating game available as a Chrome Extension and can also be played for free on the website https://doodlejump.net/. In this action-packed game, you'll take control of a lively shell as it jumps from platform to platform, encountering thrilling challenges along the way.

In "Jumping Shell," your objective is to guide the agile shell as it ascends on endless platforms without falling. You must carefully time your jumps to avoid obstacles and gaps, as a single misstep can send you plummeting down. The game tests your reflexes and agility as you navigate through a series of dynamically changing platforms.
